meline, and budget range helps me reply with something useful. Studio Details Email hello@marensolvik.studio Studio Weserstra\u00dfe 114 12045 Berlin, Germany Response Within two working days, Monday\u2013Thursday. Documents & Links For longer engagements and tenders, a current CV and selected case studies are available on request. The LinkedIn profile below lists previous in-house roles and references from past collaborators. Download CV (PDF) LinkedIn 2025 Availability The studio has limited capacity for two new identity projects starting after April 2025, with print and editorial commissions bookable through the autumn. Get in touch early if your launch date is tied to a season or exhibition opening. \u00a9 2025 Maren Solvik. All work shown by permission. Work About Process Clients Contact"}